txt.en: 'Meow! Back so soon? Well now you are up to Book III of the Epic quest series. Want me to complete that now for you? Just speak to me again and I'll flag you appropriately.
'Since you asked so nicely, when you complete this quest you'll be flagged as having completed Book III of the Epic. Have fun and be careful out there!'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book III of the Epic quest series.
